snippet.title: STW #300: Armageddon 2006
snippet.description:
It's Episode #300 of Something To Wrestle! Bruce and Conrad go back 15 years to revisit Armageddon 2006, which took on December 17, 2006, at the Richmond Coliseum in Richmond, VA. In it, we'd see John Cena and Batista take on King Booker and Finlay, Undertaker vs. Mr. Kennedy in a Last Ride Match, Gregory Helms vs. Jimmy Wang Yang for the Cruiserweight Championship, Chris Benoit vs. Chavo Guerrero for the US Championship, and much more!
